                        </aside>
                        <h3 class="title small">Precautions</h3>
                        <p>Avoid the outdoors between 5-10 a.m. and save outside activities for late afternoon or after a heavy rain, when pollen levels are lower.
                            Keep windows in your living spaces closed to lower exposure to pollen.
                            To keep cool, use air conditioners and avoid using window and attic fans.
                            </p>
                    </article>
                </section>
